        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/C:/Users/bronagh.moynihan/Desktop/Certificate%20IDD/DITA%20project/open_virtual_appliance__ova__configuration_requirements.dita" xtrc="p:11;82:12">If you deploy this type of data server, you must also deploy an Elasticsearch cluster
